    "body": "Hello @Dexaran, thank you for your contribution to the security of the space. We value bug reports and act upon whenever needed.\r\n\r\nIn this case, Iâ€™m afraid the Bug Bounty program prohibits the following:\r\n\r\n> Public disclosure of an unpatched vulnerability in an embargoed bounty\r\n\r\nMediation is a process held on Immunefi and we engage with whitehats in a constant, clear and well intentioned conversation. However, this makes it ineligible.\r\n\r\nWe can focus the conversation on what to do to fix the locked ERC20 issue, instead. Weâ€™re planning to support EIP-1363 as an alternative to this issue and weâ€™re open for alternatives. (See #3736)\r\n\r\nWeâ€™ll come back to this next Monday ðŸ‘ðŸ»",
